item.title: No idea where I want to go for these tracks
item.dc:creator: Eswyn
item.description:
So, this was an interesting project. It wasn’t the style I usually write in, it had a slow bpm, it had a darker feel, but I loved it as well as the techniques you used. I kept thinking about an upbeat drop, so that’s what I did, as well as a quiet part. I loved working on it and hope you enjoy it. Do keep up this great work. Maybe we could collab sometime? That would be awesome!
